---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="Affiliate Disclaimer"
      description={`Affiliate and earnings disclaimer for ${SITE_TITLE}.`}
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="page-main">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclaimer</h1>

      <div class="highlight">
        <strong>Short version:</strong> Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you click
        and buy, we may earn a commission — at no extra cost to you.
      </div>

      <h2>Full Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        {SITE_TITLE} participates in affiliate marketing programs. This means that when you
        click certain links on our site and make a purchase, we may receive a referral commission
        from the merchant. This is how we fund the time and research that goes into our guides.
      </p>

      <h2>Which Links Are Affiliate Links?</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate links are clearly disclosed at the top of any article that contains them
        (look for the yellow disclosure banner). Common affiliate partnerships include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Amazon product links</li>
        <li>Tool recommendations (Jungle Scout, Helium 10, Wise, Shopify, etc.)</li>
        <li>Freight and logistics services</li>
        <li>Inspection service providers</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Promise to You</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate commissions do <strong>not</strong> influence our editorial judgment. We
        recommend a product or service only if we've personally evaluated it and believe it
        provides genuine value. If we have a bad experience with something, we'll say so —
        even if it costs us commission income.
      </p>
      <p>
        We never accept payment to feature or positively review a product. If a company
        provides us with a free trial or review access, we will disclose that in the article.
      </p>

      <h2>Price Transparency</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate links do not increase the price you pay. You get the same price you'd get
        by going directly to the merchant's site. In some cases, our affiliate links may
        unlock special discounts or extended trial periods.
      </p>

      <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
      <p>
        This disclosure is provided in accordance with the U.S. Federal Trade Commission's
        16 CFR Part 255: "Guides Concerning the Use of Endorsements and Testimonials in
        Advertising."
      </p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or editorial policies,
        <a href="/contact">contact us</a> anytime.
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .page-main {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 2rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #1e293b; margin: 2rem 0 0.6rem; padding-bottom: 0.3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
  p { color: #374151; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  ul { color: #374151; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  a { color: #1d4ed8; }
  .highlight {
    background: #fffbeb;
    border: 1px solid #fde68a;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    color: #78350f;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
</style>
